@NON_EXISTENT_VOTE_ID = 369b336b8c8867f2cc165159
@USER_ID = testUser123
@ITEM_ID = product123

### Request 1: Create a vote
### Response 
### Status Code: 201
### Body: JSON object for the newly created vote
POST http://localhost:3000/generateVote HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{USER_ID}}",
  "itemId": "{{ITEM_ID}}"
}

### Request 2: Try to create a duplicate vote for the same user + item
### Response
### Status Code: 400 (or 409 depending on your backend)
### Body: {"Error": "User has already voted on this item"}
POST http://localhost:3000/generateVote HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{USER_ID}}",
  "itemId": "{{ITEM_ID}}"
}

### Request 3: Invalid request (missing itemId)
### Response
### Status Code: 400
### Body: {"Error": "Invalid request"}
POST http://localhost:3000/generateVote HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{USER_ID}}"
}

### Request 4: Retrieve all votes
### Response
### Status Code: 200
### Body: JSON array with all votes
GET http://localhost:3000/votes HTTP/1.1

### Request 5: Retrieve a single vote by ID
### Replace VOTE_ID with the _id returned in Request 1
### Response
### Status Code: 200
### Body: JSON object with correct properties
GET http://localhost:3000/votes/{{VOTE_ID}} HTTP/1.1

### Request 6: Retrieve non-existent vote by ID
### Response
### Status Code: 404
### Body: {"Error": "Not found"}
GET http://localhost:3000/votes/{{NON_EXISTENT_VOTE_ID}} HTTP/1.1

### Request 7: Update a vote (e.g., set userChoice to 1)
### Response
### Status Code: 200
### Body: JSON object with updated vote
PUT http://localhost:3000/votes/{{VOTE_ID}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{USER_ID}}",
  "itemId": "{{ITEM_ID}}",
  "userChoice": 1
}

### Request 8: Delete a vote
### Response
### Status Code: 204 (empty body)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/votes/{{VOTE_ID}} HTTP/1.1

### Request 9: Delete non-existent vote
### Response
### Status Code: 404
### Body: {"Error": "Not found"}
DELETE http://localhost:3000/votes/{{NON_EXISTENT_VOTE_ID}} HTTP/1.1
